IN RE A.W. 2018-1182 Supreme Court of Ohio. February 15, 2019

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

On motion for admission pro hac vice of Marsha L. Levick and Andrew R. Keats. Motion granted. Pursuant to Gov.Bar R. XII(4), counsel shall file a notice of permission to appear pro hac vice with the Office of Attorney Services within 30 days.
